## Create bucket
```
aws s3 mb s3://prefixes-fun-ab-3424
```

## Create folder
```
aws s3api put-object --bucket="prefixes-fun-ab-3424" --key="hello/"
```

## Create folder multiple level
```
aws s3api put-object --bucket="prefixes-fun-ab-3424" --key=""
```

## Put object
```
aws s3api put-object --bucket="prefixes-fun-ab-3424" --key="" --body="myfile.txt"
```
